{"tid":1326002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制TVB - 大家一齊回顧下星期日圍馬明嘅成果","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T02:14:18.000Z","uid":267969,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"03d880ec251400dad1e3a18fa885088f8c066aa4","tid":1326002,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"星期日，大概有30-50人，1400 紅磡 1530 沙田<br />\n小朋友表演大家好克制，主持講嘢即刻嗌口號，最後馬明上台主禮，無按原定計劃玩遊戲<br />\n<br />\n馬明上台前，Big Big Channel 直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4rWjYOX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rWjYOX.png&h=dc94e1e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬明上台後，所有人湧去採訪區嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/R3uQ5rf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR3uQ5rf.png&h=84559b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n效果超乎想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記得嗌乜口號</span></strong><br />\n1. 反對紅色媒體<br />\n2. 無綫新聞 出賣港人<br />\n3. 袁志偉 下台<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制廣告商</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「抵制廣告商」口號最重要，要上到報！<br />\n舉牌嘅記得用粗字<br />\nlead 口號嘅人，記得轉口號，等大家嘅訴求可以喺傳媒度傳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n黑警係武攻<br />\nTVB係文攻<br />\n港共政府嘅爪牙"},{"pid":"6cc85649f2f2e84829fee768317e46a059de06fe","tid":1326002,"uid":75759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcf0453c1dbce2448c1e06332ce1f597d31770aa","tid":1326002,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img 